{"data":[{"id":563313481,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563313481","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546224281,"updated_time":1546224281,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我理解题主，并且有相同经历。而且据我所知，有这样想法的人真的不少。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我高三的时候是学渣，所在班级也是学渣班。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e文科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我和我的死党的成绩都属于初中还不错，高中天天沉迷游戏啥也不会的程度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高三的时候，他买了霍金的《时间简史》《空间简史》《果壳里的宇宙》天天看，还寻思去找找爱因斯坦相对论的资料。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我呢，还好一些，想写出一部震惊文坛的小说被保送到名牌大学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想得都挺美的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可事实上后来他告诉我那些霍金的书他根本就没看懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的小说也只写了一页。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在面对高考这个巨无霸的时候，每个自命不凡的年轻人可能都会产生不切实际的想法吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可这些天马行空的想法永远只是自己骗自己的想法而已，等到高考过后，面对现实，就会清楚真实世界的运行规则。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你高中也像我一样没有好好学习，并且自认为还是一个比同龄人聪明的人，不要再犹豫了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e努力半年会让你之后的复读更加轻松。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高考带给我们伤疤，但同时也带给我们成长。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我理解题主，并且有相同经历。而且据我所知，有这样想法的人真的不少。 我高三的时候是学渣，所在班级也是学渣班。文科。我和我的死党的成绩都属于初中还不错，高中天天沉迷游戏啥也不会的程度。 高三的时候，他买了霍金的《时间简史》《空间简史》《果壳里…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1304\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan